title: 5000 Steps HIIT: Fat Burning Walk
description:
Let's stroll and burn some calories with this at-home walking programme that requires 5000 steps to burn fat. This is an aggressive, calorie-burning workout that includes some difficult routines that will engage your abs and keep your heart rate up the entire time, burning more calories. Let us go for a walk, ladies and gentlemen! ❤️💪
